                </svg>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td class="content">
                <h1 class="title">Welcome to PayMeFans</h1>
                <div class="illustration-container">
                    <!-- Placeholder for welcome illustration -->
                    <img src="/api/placeholder/300/200" alt="Welcome" class="illustration"/>
                </div>
                <p class="text">We're thrilled to have you join our creative community. Get ready to connect with amazing creators and enjoy exclusive content.</p>
                <div style="text-align: center;">
                    <a href="#" class="btn">Explore Creators</a>
                    <a href="#" class="btn secondary-btn">View Guide</a>
                </div>
                <div class="info-box">
                    <p style="margin: 0;">ðŸŽ‰ New users get 50 bonus points to start!</p>
                </div>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td class="footer">
                <div class="footer-links">
                    <a href="#">Terms</a>
                    <a href="#">Privacy</a>
                    <a href="#">Support</a>
                </div>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
